art/20050528/4923942</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n之前出post仲呃人話經濟犯罪，究竟佢講既野幾成真幾成假？<br />\n<br />\n(1)個post有唔少巴打起到新資料：<br />\n懷疑係Agentcc(田少雄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/180625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F180625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=79d7f01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://get.google.com/albumarchive/110766364975201778040/album/AF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fget.google.com%2Falbumarchive%2F110766364975201778040%2Falbum%2FAF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ay1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=520ffdda\" target=\"_blank\">https://get.google.com/albumarchive/110766364975201778040/album/AF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO</a><br />\n內有同細路女合照<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/195035_b8c5be7a33813027f06aa1a07842ed86.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F195035_b8c5be7a33813027f06aa1a07842ed86.jpg&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ay1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8485ae69\" target=\"_blank\">https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/195035_b8c5be7a33813027f06aa1a07842ed86.jpg</a><br />\n有個相簿有細路女底褲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/223025_57b1f765b4d4e7c08fca9cbe83b74e68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F223025_57b1f765b4d4e7c08fca9cbe83b74e68.jpg&h=4f8a3067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變態留言"},{"pid":"e96771f3f882ddaafedc6e466f80872aeb22e09b","tid":2248243,"uid":1